<div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn">
                
                
<lg n="1" met="āryā">
                        
                        
<l n="ab">
                                
<lb n="1" />dhik teṣān dhik teṣāṃ punar api dhig dhig dhig astu dhik teṣāṃ
                        </l>
                        
<l n="cd">
                                yeṣān na vasati hṛdaye 
<lb n="2" />k
<unclear>u</unclear>-patha-gati -vimokṣako rudraḥ 
<g type="ddanda">.</g>
                        </l>
                                                        
            </lg>
                
                                
         </div>


        
<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">               
                        
           
<p rend="stanza" n="1">
                        
<l>Woe to them! Woe to them! Again woe woe woe woe be to them</l>
                        
<l>In whose heart does not dwell the one who releases from going the wrong path: Rudra!</l> 
                </p>
        </div>
        
        
<div type="translation" xml:lang="fra" resp="part:sybr">
                
                
<p rend="stanza" n="1">
                        
<l>Malheur à ceux, malheur à ceux, et encore malheur, malheur, malheur à ceux</l>
                        
<l>Dans le cœur de qui n’habite point celui qui délivre des mauvais chemins : Rudra !</l> 
                </p>
                
        </div>
        
        
